Science, said: "We plan to sponsor annual activities to enable
more students to learn some about Tibet, especially young people
from Hong Kong and Macao.
</P>
<P>
Students from the two regions expressed their desire to learn
more about Tibet in order to make a greater contribution to the
development in Tibet.
</P>
<P>
This year's activities are jointly sponsored by the China
Qinghai-Tibet Plateau Research Center, All-China Students
Federation, Hong Kong University and a youth organization of the
Tibet Autonomous Region.  
