<HEADLINE> Semifinals Results of Toshiba Classic Tennis </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, August 2 (Xinhua) -- Following are the results
Saturday from the 450,000-dollar Toshiba Classic at the La Costa
Resort and Spa in Carlsbad, California (prifix number denotes
seeding):
</P>
<P>
